SENT IT BACK FOUR TIMES
1st: my "melted swiss and ham" was cold, the bread was stale;

2nd: the middle was warm but the flapping ends of the cheese were obviously cold, the bread was still stale;

3rd: the meat was warm but there wasn't any cheese;

4th: still a cluster f@ck!
by this time the onion rings had gotten cold, and I'd asked for ranch and mustard three times.

